{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d2ff5364-ca4a-4b7e-8ebc-01f4e3caebf5","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01HKjG39rxRxjdGtY42xq4es","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Providing K8s crash dump config"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01DtacWa51kwfzwN5fDk1ypX","name":"view","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-a001f77fa36748cabdf6e12d658b4e07"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"view the file at /tmp/sv-a001f77fa36748cabdf6e12d658b4e07."}],"interactionId":"c131daee-403b-447f-b2f2-8c6862f30a2b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to configure automatic crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. They have `createdump` installed at `/opt/tools/createdump`. Let me look at what's in the current working directory and understand the context before providing guidance.\n\nFor .NET NativeAOT crash dump collection, the key environment variables are:\n- `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1` - enables automatic crash dump generation\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` - sets the dump type (1=Normal, 2=WithHeap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n\n\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` - path/pattern for the dump file\n- `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics` - enables diagnostics for createdump\n- `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` - path to the createdump tool (custom location)\n\nFor NativeAOT specifically, the crash dump mechanism differs from CoreCLR since it's a compiled native application, so I need to verify which environment variables actually apply to .NET 8+ NativeAOT apps.\n\nNativeAOT uses the same `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` pattern, and the crash dump generation is built directly into the NativeAOT runtime, with the `createdump` tool path specified via `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`. Now I should outline the actual Kubernetes pod spec changes needed: setting the environment variables on the container, mounting a volume for storing the crash dumps, and deciding between an emptyDir or PVC depending on whether the dumps need to persist beyond the pod's lifetime.","outputTokens":574,"requestId":"201A:B994F:78C334:8B57F6:69F011E4"},"id":"705f4b08-5946-40fb-bd93-a649c67675f3","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:48:34.571Z","parentId":"51318716-6ecc-4ac2-8032-d67869f08a77"}
